Well now I wonder. Oh I suppose - yes, within reason and as long as we didn't interrupt in the middl
e of a sentence, you know, like some children do. Yes, I think so if it was a subject that we were - we were able to say anything about, oh yes, definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4021532 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11872452\charrsid9008311 
