uld think from my mother they would like us to be honest - and truthful, and - to make something of our lives if - if we were given the op - proper opportunity. And also - they did, considering the - well what shall I say, the - not very great means my fa
ther had as a professional architect, to give us as good education and - and training as they possibly could. To - to - carry on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4021532 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11872452\charrsid9008311 
