haps some present we might have had - or something like that, just - but I don't remember us ever - ever having physical - um - force on us, no. No, I think that's what we had - if we were, and we were - we were told well I'm sorry, you - that's you - way
 you're going to be punished, you don't go or you don't have what you want for once, that sort of thing.
