Oh I told you that did you, yes, I mean originally, yes, a few doors farther up and then my hus - then my father built them this lovely house. But of course Charlies died \{BLANK\} The writer, the one who wrote - lovely travel things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4021532 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11872452\charrsid9008311 Your mother would see women friends on her at home days?
