Oh quite a lot - certainly at weekends we had - when we were - especially when we were beginning to grow up, we had - oh yes, people did, they used to come quite often }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13897837\charrsid9008311 uninvited}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11872452\charrsid9008311 . Those - in those da
ys, they don't nowadays because - I think things are all too difficult, everybody and that - I mean - life is too hard all round for most people. Oh yes, they did, that was one of the things that - that's one of the things that was nice. It's a great pity
 
that doesn't happen more often, but life is so different, every - so many people are working and that sort of thing, were never working in those days. No, no, we used to love it, it was awful fun, we never knew who would come, you see. No, that was great 
fun.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4021532 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11872452\charrsid9008311 What sort of time of the day would they come?
