We were quite friendly with our one next door neighbour, the other one not so much they were a very extraordinary - an e
xtraordinary couple who lived there. Yes, I think - I think it was the - I think it was the mother and the daughter, I don't think there was a husband, I think he died. We never had much to do with them but the other next door neighbour was rather nice an
d - used to have a lot of fun together, we were all - the same age. And -
