As far as my mother was very young, and she first came to live there she was very interested in astronomy. And - when we were opposite - opposite was
 also extremely interested in it, and she loved to go and look and watch in this telescope. And - that was opposite, that was - he was very charming, he and - he was a bachelor and lived with a - lived with a maiden sister who looked after him, and I reme
m
ber him, he was very sweet. Very nice man indeed. And in the first - in the 1926 - general strike, he was very kind. He used to take father up and - up and down to town - to work you know and - oh he was very charming man, very charming. But I remember mo
ther getting so excited over this astronomy. She loved them. She was very }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13897837\charrsid9008311 interested}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11872452\charrsid9008311  in it.
\par 
