Well there might have been, might have been, oh yes, she was - and I always think it's not really anything to
 do with astrology but I think it was - such a shame that she died before she ever flew in - because - she was - she was always made about it, mad to fly. And we've all done so much of it, because my elder sister and I certainly have done masses of it, it
'
s like getting onto a train to me, but - she always wanted to and I said to my sister it's such a shame - darling mother never got the chance to fly. She must have had some feeling for the - the - up here obviously, the astronomy and - and - you know - wa
nting to fly you know. Get above the earth. But of course unfortunately she died before flying became - the common thing it is now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4021532 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11872452\charrsid9008311 Do you remember musical evenings, people getting together?
