ember whether we did so much, we were all taught - you know, to play and that but what we loved to have was sort of - our great joy when we were young was to get - round, sort of have somebody read to us. We - we loved that, we had - schoolfriend of my br
other - who - whose parents were friends of my parents you know, like that, that }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13897837\charrsid9008311 we'd}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
