Oh now, what did - oh anything - practically anything we found was interesting I think. But it was a wonderful - actually he ended up by going on the stage and - oh he was a fascin
ating person. But how we loved that, we used to sit absolutely spellbound, it's just one of the - you know, some people can read so well, and - just fascinated us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4021532 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11872452\charrsid9008311 I've hear Emlyn Williams doing Charles Dickens.
