ell - yes - in my earlier - my younger days, yes. We had about - oh I suppose half a dozen friends I had who were very keen on auction and we used to go - I've had a lot of fun that - evening - we used to go to each other's houses, but - I - I mean I was 
never a player like he would be, I mean he was a brilliant player, he really was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4021532 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11872452\charrsid9008311 Were your mother and father players too?
