 that sort of thing. But I'm rather sorry now I never learnt to play contract because - well I don't know, perhaps it's just as well because if you get - if you get caught in it - you see, when we - when auction - when contract first came in and auction f
i
nished, we moved, and all the friends I - used to play with - all scattered all over the place, and - I just never found anybody to teach me or to - to - get in contact with over it. But I'm rather sorry in many ways, 'cos I'm very fond of cards, I like t
hem.
