Oh we did a lot of the card games - of all sorts, like - yes, and all that sort of thing, Happy Families and all that and the usual ones, oh yes, as kids - as kids we loved that. I remember sitting round the table \{BLANK\}
 and all that sort of thing that all children love you know. All those sort of games we had, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4021532 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11872452\charrsid9008311 And your mother played them with you?
