be - do you remember the farthing bun or wouldn't you? Well, you know what a - it's about one quarter of the size of the great }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13897837\charrsid9008311 gallopers}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
